title: S3 Ep135: Live From Crypticon: Your Favorite Horror Stars! - Hr. 3

description: We go out to Crypticon in Minneapolis for hour three and interview some of your favorite horror stars about their favorite movie memories and paranormal experiences.  Appearing in this episode:  James Duval (Donnie Darko), Chris Sarandon(Fright Night, The Princess Bride, The Nightmare Before Christmas), Doug Jones (Hellboy, The Rise of the Silver Surfer), and John Kassir (Voice of the Crypt Keeper)
